Basic file commands

ls -- list all files
ls -l -- list files in long format
cp filename1 filename2 -- copy files
mv filename1 filename2 -- move files
diff filename1 filename2 -- compares and shows difference between the files

Basic directory commands

mkdir -- make directory
cd dirname -- change directory
pwd -- present working directory

Basic user commands

ps -u -- lists all processes
ps -u username -- lists all processes for the username
kill PID -- terminates the process


Searching commands

ff -- finds file
ff -p finds the file even without full name
grep 'regex' -- matches the regular expression
